creator: TMNK Enterprises Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Wasili is an application that has revolutionized the movement of people within the Rift Valley. Travel has never been easier, with the services of an efficient, reliable taxi at literally the tip of your fingers.

Ask for a taxi at a place and time of your convenience. Know the fare estimate to various destinations before confirming the reservation. Pay for the services through cash or mpesa.

All you need is to download the wasili application, register and voila! Your travel will never be the same again.
descriptionShort: Wasili is an ultra-convenient way of moving around in Nakuru town
